Covert Skins.name: Glock-18 | Bullet Queen
Covert Skins.desc: Menacing bullets and a War Maiden in a pink jacket have been custom painted over a yellow and black base.
Covert Skins.lore: "I'll stop shooting when you start shushing"

Covert Skins.name: M4A1-S | Player Two
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with bright colors and features animated versions of a GIGN CT and Pop Dog.

Classified Skins.name: MAC-10 | Disco Tech
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted using a pearlescent finish to resemble holographic self-adhesive vinyl. Depending on the light its appearance changes.
Classified Skins.lore: Watch when you point that thing

Classified Skins.name: MAG-7 | Justice
Classified Skins.desc: It has been custom painted using the Justice tarot card as inspiration.

Classified Skins.name: AK-47 | Phantom Disruptor
Classified Skins.desc: A mistform illusion creature has been custom painted over a matte black base.
Classified Skins.lore: "It can be whatever it wants, wherever it wants, and yet it chooses to reside with you…"

Restricted Skins.name: SSG 08 | Fever Dream
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with manic pink, blue, and purple drawings on a black base.

Restricted Skins.name: SCAR-20 | Enforcer
Restricted Skins.desc: A sunset gradient has been meticulously painted on different parts of the weapon.
Restricted Skins.lore: Automatic solutions from SYMETRY SMART GUN CORP

Restricted Skins.name: P2000 | Acid Etched
Restricted Skins.desc: A randomized multicolored pattern with a rare four-leaf clover has been applied.

Restricted Skins.name: Sawed-Off | Apocalypto
Restricted Skins.desc: A decomposing hand reaching for a bomb-like planet has been custom painted over a purple outer space background.

Restricted Skins.name: SG 553 | Darkwing
Restricted Skins.desc: A red and black custom paint job with feathers and other dark details has been applied.
Restricted Skins.lore: Eagle eyed and extremely lethal; you won't find a more dangerous flightless bird

Mil-Spec Skins.name: R8 Revolver | Bone Forged
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: The grip of this revolver has been custom painted with the remains of an ancient sea creature.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Negev | Prototype
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted in white and red, a temporary paint job while its design is finalized.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: AWP | Capillary
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: A custom paint job comprised of intricate teal and coral veins has been applied.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: The key to an agent's heart costs $4750

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MP5-SD | Desert Strike
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with a high-tech design in tan and black.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: CZ75-Auto | Distressed
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: The copper colored ceramic finish is wearing away with use.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Desert Eagle | Blue Ply
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been laminated and filled with an ash-colored grip and blue slide.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: WARNING: This is a replica and has not been tested with live ammunition

Mil-Spec Skins.name: AUG | Tom Cat
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: Its gunmetal base coat has been finished with gold highlights, rear facing arrows, and a mischievous looking cat.
